{"tid":811304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有時都幾佩服大陸","createTime":"2018-09-08T16:39:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T08:24:47.000Z","uid":197959,"like":61,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"24c1c24312a3c4376a43c47b194dc8083ab49dff","tid":811304,"uid":197959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T16:39:33.000Z","msg":"搞到身邊啲人咁井底之蛙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n早幾日同身邊啲人講起貿易戰中國唔會赢到。<br />\n屌你,個個都圍住我話中國有幾好,又吹到咩整到晶片,我心諗明明個半月前吹到咁大整到,但係依家都冇晒聲，點會整到?<br />\n<br />\n結果上網check原來收咗皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明兩邊貿易易差差三倍,點知又有個話咩中國遲下會富起來，果下真係打晒冷震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講到所有app都有監控,又吹話監控好,唔會有恐襲,真係cls,對住佢地真係,不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真心,人口老化加之前一孩,富條鐵咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e68a5767dd22f8235927e4ba7ec97a21afd8ea","tid":811304,"uid":197959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T16:41:55.000Z","msg":"仲有啲廢老,成日用移民地時候比依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你移民地想人地對你幾好,留咗個國際機場仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f4f94ed6286c8e28c74504ec8bc04aee7066da0","tid":811304,"uid":24572,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T16:45:02.000Z","msg":"因為人只會相信自己想信嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebb47b926a255ff35c17dbe9913db42c71100239","tid":811304,"uid":197959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T16:48:51.000Z","msg":"仲有依家日本關西果到<br />\n好似日本官方話冇中國嘅車救人(唔肯定)<br />\n啲人就係報紙打晒飛機,話咩中國人大愛，台灣香港人照救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係就無視之前嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b3